metadata.name: I MINTED AN OPEN EDITION AND ALL I GOT WAS THIS FUCKING JPEG.
metadata.description: I MINTED AN OPEN EDITION AND ALL I GOT WAS THIS FUCKING JPEG" is an entirely un-thought-provoking NFT artwork that pokes fun at the current trend of minting OE non-fungible tokens for digital artworks. The piece features a simple JPEG image with the caption, humorously expressing the disappointment that often comes with minting an "open edition" NFT that holds no scarcity or rarity.
